This patch series adds SBI support for RISC-V and some minor
interrupt related fixes.

Patches 1 & 2 are related to interrupt fixes.
Patches 3-5 are preparatory patches for SBI support.
Patche 6 actually adds SBI support.

Changes from v1->v2
1. Copyright & file renamings.
2. Minor nit fixes in patch 5 & 6.

The patchset is also avaialble at 
https://github.com/atishp04/xvisor-next/tree/sbi_fix_final

